high_descs: Turn around and face the counter.
Pick up the green scrub sponge.
Turn left and walk over to the stove and stand in front of it.
On the stove, put the sponge in the left-side pot, standing upright with the yellow side facing right.
Pick up the pot with the sponge still inside.
Turn right and walk over to the white table in the corner and stand in front of the brown loaves of bread.
Set the pot down on the table in front of the chair at the upper left side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot, with a scrub sponge in it, on the table.

high_descs: Turn around to face the counter.
Pick up the sponge from the right side of the counter.
Carry the sponge and turn to the left and then left again. Face the stove to the right.
Place the sponge in the pot on the front left burner of the stove.
Pick up the pot from the stove.
Carry the pot and turn to the right, then right again and around the counter. Face the table on the left side.
Place the sponge and pot on the table, to the far left side.
anns.task_desc: Move a pot and sponge to a table.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter with the toaster.
Pick up the sponge to the left of the glass.
Walk to the stove across the room.
Place the sponge in the pan on the front left burner.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn around and walk to the white table across the room.
Place the pan on the table to the left of the loaves of bread.
anns.task_desc: To move a sponge in a pan to the white table.
